videos.description: Kyra Elzy talks about how No. 5 seed UK has been battle-tested and proved it again today against the No. 12 seed Gators despite Kiara Smith's career night.
videos.headline: Elzy praises No. 5 UK for staying the course in win

videos.description: 5-seed Kentucky ends game on a 14-6 run to dispatch the 12-seed Gators 73-64, despite Kiara Smith's 36 points, advancing UK to the SEC Tournament quarterfinals.
videos.headline: Howard's 27 points fuel comeback win vs. Florida
